I thought I would throw in My 2 cents on this topic.<br>
I really like what I am seeing, and would like to share my thoughts to see what you all think.<br>
<br>
1. Loot system once in place needs to be clearly posted on the General forums of each website ( OotBS, Alliance, Dragonlayers). This will be done once it is solidified..so i know this is coming.<br>
<br>
2. Alternate loot systems in place. No offense meant..but not everyone is gonna like this system..it penalizes the casual players who are not online 24/7 like some of us are. I would like to see a separate set of loot rules that could be used on any given day whether it be a scheduled planned raid or the impromptu ones. This system could be simply random roll All. So whoever is in attendance gets a shot whether they be allied, or guests and regardless on whether they have 500 points to spend or none. It also may be used on any raid of any magnitude. I guarantee you will see tremendous support on events planned that use this system as the casual players will know they have a &quot;shot&quot; at loot.<br>
<br>
3. Each raid that is scheduled has the specific loot system to be used posted in advance. I want no questions on any future raids we do. <br>
Therefore, as an example:<br>
Hate raid, July 4th 2002. Loot system: Points. Epic drops too: Magas, Sokarxx. First BP to Azerik, Etc.<br>
This is clear...and lets players know what to expect.<br>
<br>
4. I would like, as Morale officer in OotBS..the permission to give out ( as rewards for the fun things I have planned) Points that can be used in the raids.<br>
For example..I have a naked Ogre race coming soon..it would be cool if the reward for the winner could be points. This would encourage attendance at the fun events coming up and also puts less pressure on me to try to come up with &quot;awesome prizes&quot; to events I plan. <br>
I will post specifcs on events I intend to run in the officers sections so that you all can veto or ok possible rewards i want to put in place.<br>
<br>
Well that is all i have to add to this system...I am encouraged by what I have seen..and hope you guys are interested in some of my ideas here.<br>
<br>
Naralli Ironsmith<br>
54 warrior OotBS <p></p><i></i></td></tr></table><br><font color=#0000FF>- </font><a href=http://pub42.ezboard.com/ballianceraidforum>Alliance Raid Forum</a><font color=#0000FF> - </font><a href=http://pub42.ezboard.com/fallianceraidforumfrm6>Officer and Administration</a> <font color=#0000FF> - </font><br><br><table border=0 align=center><tr><td align=center><a href="http://login.ezboard.com/BBSSystem.showUserPaymentScreen" target="_blank">Upgrade your account to ezSupporter...</a></td><td><img src="http://www.ezboard.com/image/spacer.gif" width=15 height=1 border=0></td><td align=center><a href="http://login.ezboard.com/BBSSystem.showUserPaymentScreen" target="_blank">...and never see another ad or pop-up again</a></td></tr></table><CENTER><!-- START BOTTOM AD SCRIPT -->
